    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit features a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and upgraded throttle actuators. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity with a functional M-Variable differential and Electronic Damping Control (EDC) providing excellent lateral stability. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its driver-status, the powertrain delivers a linear torque curve and an 8,400 RPM redline without hesitation. Recent fluid analysis confirms healthy internals, making this a prime candidate for a purist seeking uncompromised Bavarian engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
