    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and comfort, making it an ideal choice for a discerning driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only minor road-wear consistent with its age and mileage. Inside, the cabin feels fresh and inviting, featuring premium upholstery that shows minimal signs of use and a full suite of functional electronics, including the infotainment and climate control systems. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it starts reliably, shifts smoothly through all gears, and has benefitted from a recent comprehensive service including fluid flushes and a brake inspection. I have kept a detailed log of all maintenance performed during my ownership to ensure its longevity. This is a solid, reliable car that has been cared for with pride and is ready for its next chapter without any immediate service needs.",
