      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid, reliable shape. It\u2019s clean, runs like a dream, and has plenty of life left in it! Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out on a road trip, this beauty is ready to go. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
