    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features a high-pressure Double-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M Differential Lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The cooling system has been overhauled with a high-flow water pump, and the suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers to maintain factory-spec kinematics. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain integrity and valve clearances are meticulously maintained for the enthusiast who prioritizes driving dynamics.",
